ix.Locale:Build("en")

item.porn_magazine1 				= "FleshCoin™ Catalog. \"Custodian\" Series"
item.porn_magazine1.desc 		= "A worn glossy paper catalog. The glossy pages capture women whose bodies are the pinnacle of Universal Union engineering. Every curve is a perfect arc of polished synthetic fabric. In some photos they stand in combat stances, demonstrating the power of their thigh muscles; in others they have opened technical access panels on their hips or chest, exposing dark wires and flickering dark matter energy cells beneath the skin. The text describes \"optimal operator stress relief modes\" and \"enhanced sensitivity interfaces\"."
item.porn_magazine2 				= "FleshCoin™ Catalog. \"Special Edition\" Series"
item.porn_magazine2.desc 		= "A worn glossy paper catalog. Inside are vulgar staged photos. The magazine visualizes approved methods for maintaining the moral and physiological tone of personnel, using modern Universal Union synthetic models developed jointly with FleshCoin™ Corporation. The manual emphasizes the functionality of the process and its entirely beneficial purpose for increasing combat effectiveness and preventing desertion."
item.porn_magazine3 				= "FleshCoin™ Catalog. \"Replicant\" Series"
item.porn_magazine3.desc 		= "A worn glossy paper catalog. The text in technical jargon praises the \"Organic-Synthetic Assimilation Program\" — a new turn of evolution under the guidance of FleshCoin™ Corporation. The caption reads: \"The future grows within us. Your productivity is its nutrient medium.\" The synthetic body is presented as an incubator, and pregnancy as an industrial process for growing the next generation of loyal citizens or, more likely, perfect soldiers. Evokes not tenderness, but chilling horror."
item.porn_magazine4 				= "FleshCoin™ Catalog. \"Zen's Joy\" Series"
item.porn_magazine4.desc 		= "The glossy spread shocks at first glance with advertisements for extravagant relaxation products. These \"toys\" replicate the form of parasites with frightening anatomical accuracy: chitinous plates, claws, and member-like appendages. The ad slogan reads: \"LIVING HORROR, TRANSFORMED INTO ABSOLUTE PLEASURE — NOW YOUR BEST LOVER\". The peak of perverse consumerism in the post-Combine world. Fear of lethal fauna transformed into a tool for momentary pleasure. Evokes a mixed feeling of disgust, curiosity, and deepest longing for a world where horror remained simply horror, not a commodity."
item.porn_magazine5 				= "FleshCoin™ Catalog. \"7X\" Series"
item.porn_magazine5.desc 		= "A worn glossy paper catalog. Contains a selection of photos from standard \"mechanical stimulation\" points for Civil Protection employees at Universal Union facilities. A standardized device known in soldier slang as the \"Loyalty Slot\" is mounted into a sterile wall finished with Universal Union metal. A synthetic woman—or rather, her pelvic section—is chained to the port on the other side: perfectly symmetrical, devoid of any anatomical details except the functional connection port. The catalog captures the non-public side of service synthetic life."
item.porn_magazine6 				= "FleshCoin™ Catalog. \"Lacto-Genesis\" Series"
item.porn_magazine6.desc 		= "A worn glossy paper catalog. The catalog is part of an official prospectus demonstrating the efficiency of agro-industrial corporations under Universal Union control. Bio-mechanical modules are installed in rows in a deep workshop. In each is secured a synthetic donor woman of the \"Lacto-Genesis\" series, devoid of any individual traits, representing ideal biological machines. Milking devices are attached to the chest, extracting synthetic nutrient fluid rich in proteins and nutrients (designated in documents as \"Substrate-7\"). The text explains: \"This technology has allowed a 300%% increase in production efficiency and a 99.8%% reduction in bacteriological contamination risk compared to outdated production methods.\""
item.porn_magazine7 				= "FleshCoin™ Catalog. \"C8\" Series"
item.porn_magazine7.desc 		= "An expensive magazine printed on quality synthetic paper. The shot is staged and stylized: two high-ranking officials in a luxurious office with a panoramic view of the night city. Their uniforms are impeccable but shot from the waist up, exposing their chests. The shine of polished Universal Union emblem plaques on their collars contrasts with the soft light falling on their skin. They don't look at each other—their gazes are directed at the viewer, full of cold superiority and awareness of their inviolability. The text on the page, set in elegant type, reads: \"Power is the strongest aphrodisiac. Available only to the chosen few.\" The magazine isn't for everyone—it's for those like them. A hint that real eroticism isn't the body, but status, and only those already part of this \"elite\" can purchase this edition."
item.porn_magazine8 				= "FleshCoin™ Catalog. \"Aphrodite\" Series"
item.porn_magazine8.desc 		= "A worn glossy paper catalog. The cover shows a close-up of the hip module of the \"Aphrodite-X7\" model. The synthetic skin perfectly mimics the texture of living flesh but has no pores or imperfections. The light falls to emphasize flawless symmetry, engineering precision of lines, and hidden magnetic points for accessory attachment. But it is precisely this perfection that betrays artificiality. Not the slightest asymmetry, no hint of cellulite or natural skin texture. This is temptation created in a laboratory, a product of design, not nature. The slogan in the corner, set in gleaming type, reads: \"The illusion of perfection. On your request.\""
item.porn_magazine9 				= "FleshCoin™ Catalog. \"Perfection\" Series"
item.porn_magazine9.desc 		= "A worn glossy paper catalog. On the cover—a synthetic woman standing in a neutral pose against an absolutely white background. Every line of her body is the product of the most complex mathematical calculations aimed at creating ideal proportions: the golden ratio in the curve of her waist, flawless symmetry of hips, smooth skin devoid of pores, scars, or moles. This catalog advertises corporate services. On the back in small print: \"The same model awaits you at any official Union brothel. The corporation is not responsible for psychological dependency.\""
item.porn_magazine10 				= "FleshCoin™ Catalog. \"Promise\" Series"
item.porn_magazine10.desc 		= "A worn glossy paper catalog. On the cover—a perfectly calibrated \"Promise\" brand pleasure machine demonstrates the workflow of client service. The model's visor gaze is empty—savings on facial animations, but who looks at the eyes when her perfectly accentuated lips service the male interface in sufficient detail? This catalog advertises corporate services that long ago stopped selling sex and now sell the sensation of power over something that looks almost human but is more submissive than any flesh. On the back in small print: \"Services provided until complete component wear. The corporation is not responsible for psychological dependency.\""
